In this #TackleTipTuesday video brought to you by @MercuryMarine, two-time Bassmaster Elite Series Champion @jamiehartmanprofishing talks about one of the most effective techniques to catch big smallmouth across the country. Hartman maps out his entire Carolina Rig setup and a few key aspects he feels are important for catching smallmouth on this setup. 
#Bassmaster #BASSElite #BassFishing

node.title: The most underrated technique for catching BIG Smallmouth

node.text:
Winning a Bassmaster Classic requires three days of execution, bait selection and sometimes an area of the lake all to yourself. In 2021, @hankcherryfishing displayed a few of those as he utilized a couple different lures and select areas to win at Lake Ray Roberts. 

Cherry used the brand new  @BerkleyFishing  Stunna jerkbait he designed as well as a key bait change late on Day 3 when he chose to flip with a Berkley Pit Boss. 
#Bassmaster #BassmasterClassic #BassFishing

node.title: Two lures that helped Hank Cherry win back-to-back Classics

#Bassmaster #BASSElite #Top100 #BassFishing

Hartman maps out his entire Carolina Rig setup and a few key aspects he feels are important for catching smallmouth on this setup. 
#Bassmaster #BASSElite #BassFishing

node.text:
Winning a Bassmaster Classic requires three days of execution, bait selection and sometimes an area of the lake all to yourself. In 2021, @hankcherryfishing displayed a few of those as he utilized a couple different lures and select areas to win at Lake Ray Roberts. 

Cherry used the brand new  @BerkleyFishing  Stunna jerkbait he designed as well as a key bait change late on Day 3 when he chose to flip with a Berkley Pit Boss. 
#Bassmaster #BassmasterClassic #BassFishing
